    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute time capsule: this vehicle is in true mint condition, looking and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with original paint that has been meticulously clay-barred and ceramic coated. There are zero dings, scratches, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats still retain their factory-fresh scent and firm bolsters, with no signs of wear or creasing. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions perfectly. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. This car has been strictly garage-kept, never smoked in, and driven only in fair weather. It comes complete with all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a comprehensive folder of service records. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless example of automotive excellence.",
